  <brief_title>Clinical Trial of Minimally Invasive Robotic Spine Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Comparative Trial of Minimally Invasive Robotic vs. Freehand in Short Adult Degenerative Spinal Fusion Surgeries</official_title>
  <sponsors>
